channel.title: [Spermy Factory] Android apps
channel.description:
Been experimenting with android development the last days together with some other guy. Made our first app with the purpose of learning, but at least the concept is original. .. I think. You gotto guess whether the person you see is a girl or a trap (guy looking like a girl) There's some stats and preferences and stuff.
You can find our apps when searching for "spermy factory" which is our developers name on the play store. As the name shows we ain't going for serious stuff, just having fun and hoping that people can enjoy our work, now or in the future.
Some feedback is always welcome, but as we're just getting into it there's no need to say how bad it looks, we know.
